Module kivakit.primitive.collections
Package com.telenav.kivakit.primitive.collections.map

Interface PrimitiveScalarMap

All Known Implementing Classes:
IntToByteMap, IntToIntMap, IntToLongMap, LongToByteMap, LongToIntMap, LongToLongMap, SplitIntToIntMap, SplitLongToByteMap, SplitLongToIntMap, SplitLongToLongMap
public interface PrimitiveScalarMap
A map from one scalar primitive to another, like LongToLongMap or IntToByteMap. This interface allows all such maps to be treated the same, by widening the key and value to a long primitive.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
